Paper: hep-th/9402111

Date: 1994-02-18

Title: Separation of variables for the quantum relativistic Toda lattices

Authors: V.B.Kuznetsov and A.V.Tsiganov

Comments: 13 pp., AMSTex, Report 94-07, Mathematical preprint series,

University of AmsterdamWe consider quantum analogs of the relativistic Toda lattices and give new$2\times 2$ $L$-operators for these models. Making use of the variableseparation the spectral problem for the quantum integrals of motion is reducedto solving one-dimensional separation equations.